@startuml logout_user_sequence_diagram
title Sequence Diagram: User Logout (Clearing HttpOnly Cookie )

actor User
participant "Frontend (React SPA)" as FE
participant "Auth Controller\n(Backend API)" as AuthCtrl

== User Initiates Logout ==

User -> FE: Click "Logout"
FE -> AuthCtrl: POST /logout\n(with session cookie)


AuthCtrl -> FE: Set-Cookie: session=; HttpOnly\n200 OK
note right of AuthCtrl
  Uses CookieUtil.clearJwtCookie()
end note

FE -> User: Show Login button

@enduml
